fseReportingDesc: Enter dates of supply and kWh usage for compliance reporting. The 'Set default values' button will only apply to the visible rows. Use the site name filter and/or paging to assist in setting date variances.
reportingResponsibilityInfo: Report dates of supply for your final supply equipment (FSE).
Organization: Enter your organization name unless you are reporting FSE that you have received allocated responsibility. In this case, enter the utility account holder's organization name.
Enter the billing address in the Notes field if it is different than the equipment address. Also, enter an explanation in the Notes field if you select 'Other' from any of the select options.
saveConfirmation: You have validation errors. Do you want to save anyway?
postalCodeError: Please enter a valid postal code.
scheduleUpdated: Final supply equipment schedule updated successfully
